{"id": "pos004", "name": "Cam_Noah_693_05_11", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "Sings"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I have the singing part nailed down already... but I'm still nervous... after I signed, I will probably meet more strangers and fans...\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "... Tuner-san, project an audience for me.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Audience projected</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Wow... this is so realistic...\nH, hello everyone... My name is...\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">Hello everyone!</font> I'm Aroma! <font size=\"1.8\">I, I'm f... fifteen...</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "No good... still really nervous; my voice becomes weird... this is just a projection too...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Fight on! Fight on!</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yes... can't give up here. Sis Helena is working hard for me as well. I have to keep going... <font size=\"3.5\">YIKES!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... It's me.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah... you scared me. I thought there was nobody at home...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I'm sorry. I came back to... get some stuff. Did I scare you?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Umm... a little. Have you been standing there... for a long time?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... No. I just happen to pass by and was wondering who are you talking to.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Did you hear me...? That's so embarrassing...\nI am practicing how to speak normally in front of a large crowd...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You speak very normally right now though?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "That's because it's you...\nIf its other people, especially males...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... Speaking of this, it reminds me of our first meeting. That time, I visited your home with Helena. You ran away the instant you saw me, like a scaredy cat. Hahaha.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Stop it. Don't talk about that... it was so awkward back then.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You can talk to me normally right now, so I can't be your practice partner anymore. What a shame.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yeah... it's fine. Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Your sister is having a meeting at Mono and might return home really late today. How about we have dinner outside today?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Eh? Didn't you come back to get something? Don't you have to go back to work?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Haha... so you really don't want to have dinner with me?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Eh? No, that's not what I mean...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "I was kidding. I can schedule my breaks freely after I was promoted to director. I found a pretty good restaurant on the 47th floor. Dinner's on me. Come.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Ok... then let me change my clothes. Thank you for the meal!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You're welcome.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "... I will be waiting for you.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "歌うことには慣れてきたけど……でもやっぱり緊張するな……\nこれから、知らない人とかお客さんとかにいっぱい会うことになるんだよね……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……チューナーくん、お客さんを映して。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>観客ヲ 投影シマシタ</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "わぁ……本物みたい……\nこっこんにちは……Aromaで……す……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">こんにちは！</font>Aromaです！<font size=\"1.8\">今年で15……15歳……</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ダメだぁ……やっぱり緊張する……\n声も裏返っちゃってるし……\nただの映像なのに……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>ガンバレ！ガンバレ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……くじけちゃダメだよね。\nお姉ちゃんが私のためにあんなに頑張ってくれてるんだもん。\n私も頑張らないと……<font size=\"3.5\">きゃあ！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……僕だよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noahさん……ビックリしたぁ。\n家には誰もいないと思ってたから……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ごめんね。\n忘れ物を取りに……ね。\n驚かせちゃったかな？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "あ……ちょっとだけ。\nずっとそこに……？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……いや。ちょうど通りかかっただけだよ。\n誰と話してるのかなって思ってね。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "えぇ……聞かれてたなんて……\n恥ずかしい……\n今、大勢の前で話す練習をしていたの……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "今は普通に話せてるよ？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "それはNoahさんだから……\n他の人だと…特に男の人の前では全然ダメなの……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……そういえば、はじめて会った時は、Helenaの後ろに隠れて姿を見せてくれなかったね。ハハハ\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "もう…！そのことは言わないで……恥ずかしいから。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "もう僕には慣れてしまったみたいだから、話す練習相手にはなれないね。\n残念だ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……大丈夫。ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "お姉ちゃんは事務所へ打ち合わせに行っていて、帰りが遅くなるみたいだ。\nご飯でも食べに行くかい？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "え？忘れ物は？\nお仕事戻らなくていいの？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "ハハ……そんなに僕とご飯食べるのはイヤ？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ぇえ？そんなこと……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "冗談だよ。チーフになってから、自由が利くんだ。\n47階でいい店を見つけたんだけど、一緒にどうかな？ごちそうするよ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……着替えてくる！ありがとう！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いいえ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……待ってるね。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "歌聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唱的部份已經很熟練了……但是緊張……簽約以後會遇到更多陌生人跟觀眾吧……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……喇叭君，投影觀眾給我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>觀眾 已投影</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "哇……好逼真……\n大、大家好……我叫……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">大家好！</font>我叫 Aroma！<font size=\"1.8\">今年十……十五……</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不行……還是好緊張，聲音也變得好奇怪……只是投影就這樣……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>加油！加油！</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不能洩氣，姊姊也為了我在努力，我要加油……<font size=\"3.5\">哇！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……是我。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah……嚇我一跳，我以為家裡沒人……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "抱歉，我回來……拿東西，嚇到妳了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "呃……有一點，你站在那邊……很久了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……沒有，我剛好經過，想說妳在跟誰講話。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "被聽到了……？好丟臉……\n我在練習怎樣在人多的地方正常說話……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳現在說話很正常啊？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那是因為是你……\n其他人的話，尤其是男生……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……說起來我想到我們第一次見面，那時候跟 Helena 回妳們家，妳像貓一樣一溜煙就躲起來了，哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "討厭，別說了啦……好糗。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "現在能跟我正常對話，那我沒辦法當妳練習的對象了，真可惜。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……沒關係啦，謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "你姊去單聲開會可能會很晚才回來，要不要我們出去吃晚餐？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？你不是回來拿東西嗎？不用回去上班？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……這麼不想跟我吃飯？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？不是啦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "開玩笑的，升上主任後就能自由排休了。\n我在 47 層找到一間還不錯的餐廳，我請妳，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……那我換個衣服，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不用客氣。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我等妳。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "노래 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "노래는 확실히 연습하고 있지만..... 하지만 긴장하는 습관은 아직..... 계약하고 나면 더 많은 관중들과 낯선 사람들 앞에 서게 될 텐데....\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……튜너 군. 내 앞에 관중들 화면 좀 띄어줄래?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>관중 화면 송출</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "와…… 꼭 진짜 같아……\n여, 여러분 안녕하세요.... 제 이름은....\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">여러분 안녕하세요! </font>Aroma 입니다! <font size=\"1.8\">올해로 열 다섯......</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "안돼…… 아직도 긴장이 풀리지 않아. 목소리도 오히려 이상하게 들리고.... 빔프로젝터 화면만 띄웠을 뿐인데도 이렇게 긴장하면....\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "<i>할 수 있다! 할 수 있다!</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응……여기서 포기할 순 없어. 언니도 나를 위해 이렇게 노력하고 있는데... 나도 빨리 힘을 내서.... <font size=\"3.5\">꺄아악!</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……나다.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah 씨…… 너무 놀랬어요.... 집안에 아무도 없는 줄 알았는데……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "미안하구나. 놓고간 물건이 있어서... 많이 놀랐니?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아……조, 조금요. 거기에.... 계속 서 계셨어요?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……아니, 지금 막 지나가고 있던 참이였어. 지금 누구랑 얘기하고 있던 건지 물어보려던 참이었는데.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아아.... 다 들렸나 보군요……너무 창피해……\n지금 많은 사람들 앞에서 말하는 연습을 하고 있었어요...........\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "지금은 말을 편하게 잘하고 있잖니?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "그건 Noah씨니깐....\n다른 사람이랑은 말을 잘 못하겠어요... 특히 다른 남자분들하고는…\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……하하. 듣다보니 예전에 우리 처음 만났을 때가 생각나는구나. 그때 Helena와 함께 너희 집에 갔었을 때 꼭 고양이처럼 뒤로 숨던 모습이 떠오르네. 하하하.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아휴 정말! 그 이야긴 하지 마세요....\n창피하단 말이에요.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "이젠 나하고는 편하게 대화할 수 있게 된 것 같구나. 그렇게되면 네 대화 연습상대가 될 수 없겠는데, 아쉽게 됐군.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네…… 괜찮아요. 고마워요.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "네 언니는 지금 모노에서 회의 중이라고 늦게 온다고 하더구나. 저녁은 같이 나가서 먹는 게 어떻겠니?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네? 방금 놓고 간 물건이 있어서 돌아오셨다면서요? 다시 회사로 가야 하는 거 아니에요?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "하하…… 나와 밥 먹는 게 싫은가 보구나?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네? 아니, 그런 뜻이 아닌데...……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "하하. 농담이라고. 주임으로 승진한 뒤부턴 자유롭게 휴가를 배정할 수 있게 되었거든. 47에 괜찮은 식당 하나 찾았는데, 같이 가자꾸나. 내가 살 테니.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네…… 그럼 지금 옷 갈아입을게요! 고마워요!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "고맙기는.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "문을 닫는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……기다릴게.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "歌聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唱的部份已經很熟練了……但是緊張……簽約以後會遇到更多陌生人跟觀眾吧……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……喇叭君，投影觀眾給我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>觀眾 已投影</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "哇……好逼真……\n大、大家好……我叫……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">大家好！</font>我叫 Aroma！<font size=\"1.8\">今年十……十五……</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不行……還是好緊張，聲音也變得好奇怪……只是投影就這樣……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>加油！加油！</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不能洩氣，姊姊也為了我在努力，我要加油……<font size=\"3.5\">哇！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……是我。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah……嚇我一跳，我以為家裡沒人……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "抱歉，我回來……拿東西，嚇到妳了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "呃……有一點，你站在那邊……很久了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……沒有，我剛好經過，想說妳在跟誰講話。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "被聽到了……？好丟臉……\n我在練習怎樣在人多的地方正常說話……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳現在說話很正常啊？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那是因為是你……\n其他人的話，尤其是男生……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……說起來我想到我們第一次見面，那時候跟 Helena 回妳們家，妳像貓一樣一溜煙就躲起來了，哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "討厭，別說了啦……好糗。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "現在能跟我正常對話，那我沒辦法當妳練習的對象了，真可惜。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……沒關係啦，謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "你姊去單聲開會可能會很晚才回來，要不要我們出去吃晚餐？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？你不是回來拿東西嗎？不用回去上班？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……這麼不想跟我吃飯？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？不是啦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "開玩笑的，升上主任後就能自由排休了。\n我在 47 層找到一間還不錯的餐廳，我請妳，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……那我換個衣服，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不用客氣。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我等妳。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["PAFF_Singing_02", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "唱的部份已经很熟练了……但是紧张……签约以后会遇到更多陌生人跟观众吧……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……喇叭君，投影观众给我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>观众 已投影</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "哇……好逼真……\n大、大家好……我叫……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos0401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "<font size=\"3.5\">大家好！ </font>我叫 Aroma！ <font size=\"1.8\">今年十……十五……</font>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不行……还是好紧张，声音也变得好奇怪……只是投影就这样……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>加油！加油！ </i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……不能泄气，姊姊也为了我在努力，我要加油……<font size=\"3.5\">哇！ ？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……是我。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Noah……吓我一跳，我以为家里没人……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "抱歉，我回来……拿东西，吓到妳了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "呃……有一点，你站在那边……很久了吗？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……没有，我刚好经过，想說妳在跟谁讲话。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "被听到了……？好丢脸……\n我在练习怎样在人多的地方正常说话……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳现在说话很正常啊？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "那是因为是你……\n其他人的话，尤其是男生……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……说起来我想到我们第一次见面，那时候跟 Helena 回妳们家，妳像猫一样一溜烟就躲起来了，哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "讨厌，别说了啦……好糗。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "现在能跟我正常对话，那我没办法当妳练习的对象了，真可惜。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……没关系啦，谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "你姊去单声开会可能会很晚才回来，要不要我们出去吃晚餐？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？你不是回来拿东西吗？不用回去上班？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "哈哈……这么不想跟我吃饭？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦？不是啦……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "开玩笑的，升上主任后就能自由排休了。\n我在 47 层找到一间还不错的餐厅，我请妳，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……那我换个衣服，谢谢！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不用客气。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "关门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……我等妳。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}